0c9b7","tid":274940,"uid":62851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:45:26.000Z","msg":"唔超頻點解唔好上高頻ram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d1f1c313422012692b64c9d26bef8cfea6cd51","tid":274940,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有咩底板同ssd介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你筆直都係用mx300最岩<br />\n底板求奇啦<br />\n你都唔會超到上3.9或4g<br />\n唔好選msi就得<br />\n然後自己睇返塊板要咩ram</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔好msi？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n料差同佢開機自檢太長，最快都20至30秒<br />\n講緊最快</blockquote><br />\n料差？RAM用料好過其他牌子同價底板好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自檢長就真"},{"pid":"602c830f88608166c5b50791dba1325d81579be3","tid":274940,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有咩底板同ssd介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你筆直都係用mx300最岩<br />\n底板求奇啦<br />\n你都唔會超到上3.9或4g<br />\n唔好選msi就得<br />\n然後自己睇返塊板要咩ram</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔好msi？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n料差同佢開機自檢太長，最快都20至30秒<br />\n講緊最快</blockquote><br />\n料差？RAM用料好過其他牌子同價底板好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自檢長就真</blockquote><br />\nP.S. 講緊千四蚊嗰塊x370，b350唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa56c5e7a815c6e4f4e50c5ee4354fc47e141357","tid":274940,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔超頻點解唔好上高頻ram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為高頻ram原本都係行2133<br />\n一定要超頻，入bios拉返上去至得<br />\n甚至有機會要加電壓同CL至上到2933以上<br />\n（開DOCP有機會著唔到機）<br />\n<br />\n所以冇心超頻不如買返原生2133或者2400嗰啲RAM"},{"pid":"4976e571044a637dcad9f411e9082f60b2b2ed9d","tid":274940,"uid":81059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有咩底板同ssd介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你筆直都係用mx300最岩<br />\n底板求奇啦<br />\n你都唔會超到上3.9或4g<br />\n唔好選msi就得<br />\n然後自己睇返塊板要咩ram</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔好msi？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n料差同佢開機自檢太長，最快都20至30秒<br />\n講緊最快</blockquote><br />\n料差？RAM用料好過其他牌子同價底板好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自檢長就真</blockquote><br />\nP.S. 講緊千四蚊嗰塊x370，b350唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都識講370<br />\n咁唔通我話asrock最好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爸打你咁風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}